<br>
Last night, I happened to sell 3 poisons. 2 went to one gent, 1 to another. During this time, I had someone ask me how much, I said 2k, he started laughing and said he would never pay that. To each his own. The Gent who bought 2, said this was the best deal he's seen, normally sell for 3-5k by other Rogues. 10 min later, the gent who was laughing bought my 3rd poison.<br>
<br>
If I were offered 20-40 Salts, I might take it for 1 poison. <br>
<br>
I charge this much as I know what I have put into the skill to get this high. I didn't PL my skill up as a few people might have done. I sat down is spent the plat and worked my skill up with 100% loss on plat. After making a poison, I would apply it, not selling it back. Make 250, Apply 213.  <p><FONT face="Verdana">/who all</FONT><br>
