<br>
&quot;All combines have at least a 5% chance of failing, whether the item is trivial or not. No stat buff<br>
will affect the chance of success -- it is calculated by a formula that includes your skill level and the<br>
difficulty of the item.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
STR has only been said to be a modifier in getting a skill increase in smithing, it does not increase the chance of a success.   <br>
